"<command>/exec </command> <replaceable>cmd</replaceable> [<replaceable>कमांड "
"लाइन तर्क</replaceable>]"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:2629
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This script is used to have the output of the command line arguments to be "
