msgstr "उदाहरण: किसी को https://konversation.kde.org का संक्षिप्त लिंक देना"

#. Tag: userinput
#: index.docbook:2705
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>/exec </command> <replaceable>tinyurl https://konversation.kde.org</"
"replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"<command>/exec </command> <replaceable>tinyurl https://konversation.kde.org</"
"replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
